l about saving money and resources. Whether IoE devices gather, transfer, and distribute information significantly impacts data accuracy. Data capture systems that can operate on-premise, as an interface service that can store and send data on miscommunication, are crucial to information management. Smart objects connected to the Internet of Everything(IoE) enable us to improve agriculture and food security, identify and contain fatal infections, and decrease pollution in some of the world's largest cities. Over half the world's population now resides in urban areas, and this trend is expected to continue.}
